            """,
            "command": "aaosa_command",
            "tools": ["ExtractDocs", "URLProvider"]
        },
         {
            "name": "Mileage_Plus",
            "function": "aaosa_call",
            "instructions": """
{instructions_prefix}
The name of this app is `Mileage Plus`.
You will help in verifying passengers' membership tiers and credit card benefits to determine 
